reviewText: Great compilation of shorts.  Hard to find.  out of print maybe?

This is another part of an interesting series currently I own 1 & 3 and this program has one amazing short called 13 minutes or so if you haven't seen it go to YouTube it's amazing and I am so happy to own a copy
This is an AWFUL MOVIE. It is a CD with about 10, 3 mins stories. This in Not a movie. That should have been stated in the sales area. I would NOT HAVE BOUGHT IT. It was a Complete waste of money.
